      "title": "SCAD recognised at Abu Dhabi Excellence Awards",
      "excerpt": "Statistics Centre — Abu Dhabi honoured for strategic impact and ranked 4th among government entities in the Abu Dhabi Award for Excellence in Government Performance.",
      "readMore": "Read full announcement",
      "close": "Close",
      "body": "Winners of the Abu Dhabi Award for Excellence in Government Performance were announced under the patronage of His Highness Sheikh Khaled bin Mohamed bin Zayed Al Nahyan, Crown Prince of Abu Dhabi and Chairman of the Abu Dhabi Executive Council.\n\nStatistics Centre — Abu Dhabi (SCAD) was recognised with the Strategic Impact Initiatives Award in the Collaborative Initiatives Awards category, reflecting strong partnership across Strategy and Planning and more than thirty-six institutional partners.\n\nSCAD also achieved fourth place among thirty-seven participating entities in the Abu Dhabi Award for Excellence in Government Performance — a testament to our commitment to improve, innovate and create meaningful impact.\n\nTogether we continue working as one system to deliver better outcomes for Abu Dhabi."
